1348
01:30:29,490 --> 01:30:30,990
There's no other way to say this.

1349
01:30:34,000 --> 01:30:35,000
I'm you.

1350
01:30:38,000 --> 01:30:39,040
I have to be quick.

1351
01:30:39,880 --> 01:30:42,300
Attached to this message,
are detailed construction

1352
