01:32:13,220 --> 01:32:14,220


1380
01:32:21,850 --> 01:32:25,570


1381
01:32:28,650 --> 01:32:29,820


1382
01:32:34,780 --> 01:32:38,450
Three... two... one...

1383
01:32:38,910 --> 01:32:39,910
mark.

1384
01:32:40,790 --> 01:32:43,830


1385
01:32:46,960 --> 01:32:49,510


1386
01:32:51,630 --> 01:32:53,630


